WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.000
Now you have to enter your mobile number here and click on the gate OTP.

2
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:09.000
Then an OTP will be sent to your mobile number here.

3
00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:11.000
What to do with that OTP, put it in it.

4
00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:16.000
As soon as we fill up the OTP, it will automatically redirect it and take it forward.

5
00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
And here it is giving us the option to select our email id.

6
00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:28.000
So whichever email id you want to make your 5paisa app from, what to do with that email id, you have to select it from here.

7
00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:32.000
You can see all the names in your email id.

8
00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:34.000
If your name is correct then it is fine.

9
00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:39.000
If your name is wrong then remove the name and put the correct name in it.

10
00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:42.000
By looking at your Aadhar card or PAN card.

11
00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:45.000
Then what you have to do is come down and see here.

12
00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:48.000
There is a small box here.

13
00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:53.000
Click on it and then click on fetch my PAN details.

14
00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:56.000
Now see here, your PAN card number is asking for you.

15
00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:59.000
Enter your PAN card number.

16
00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:07.000
As soon as you enter the PAN card number, the name will come automatically.

17
00:01:07.000 --> 00:01:11.000
Enter your date of birth.

18
00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:13.000
Click on Continue.

19
00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:21.000
The address will be automatically displayed.

20
00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:26.380
Click on the above address to continue.

21
00:01:26.380 --> 00:01:37.898
Now you have to link your bank account There are two options for link One is to pay 1 rupee per month through UPI

22
00:01:37.898 --> 00:01:40.898
The other is to link manually.

23
00:01:40.898 --> 00:01:44.898
Click on the link and you can link manually.

24
00:01:44.898 --> 00:01:51.898
You have to select UPI link through UPI.

25
00:01:51.898 --> 00:01:54.898
Click on the proceed option.

26
00:01:54.898 --> 00:02:00.898
Once you click on it, all the UPI's will be launched.

27
00:02:00.898 --> 00:02:04.898
You have to select anyone and pay a simple one rupee.

28
00:02:04.898 --> 00:02:06.898
Your bank account will be linked directly.

29
00:02:06.898 --> 00:02:11.898
As soon as you complete the payment, your bank account will be successfully added.

30
00:02:11.898 --> 00:02:13.898
Then the next step will come.

31
00:02:13.898 --> 00:02:16.898
What to do here, see, it is asking about disability.

32
00:02:16.898 --> 00:02:19.898
So what you have to do is close it.

33
00:02:19.898 --> 00:02:21.898
Click on close, it will be closed.

34
00:02:21.898 --> 00:02:23.898
And this type of option will open and come.

35
00:02:23.898 --> 00:02:27.898
Now it is asking you to select your gender from here.

36
00:02:27.898 --> 00:02:29.898
Marital status is asking.

37
00:02:29.898 --> 00:02:35.898
If you are married, then you have not been married, then you have to select unmarried and do next.

38
00:02:35.898 --> 00:02:39.898
Now here you are being asked what work you do in the private sector.

39
00:02:39.898 --> 00:02:48.898
Government service, professional, housewife, any other work, student, retired, any business you have, whatever you are, you can select from it.

40
00:02:48.898 --> 00:03:28.577
Select the source of income Active

41
00:03:28.797 --> 00:03:33.797
Click on submit option.

42
00:03:33.797 --> 00:03:40.797
Now click on selfie option.

43
00:03:40.797 --> 00:03:45.797
Click on selfie option.

44
00:03:45.797 --> 00:03:50.797
Click on selfie option.

45
00:03:50.797 --> 00:03:53.597
After clicking the selfie, you will upload the video.

46
00:03:53.597 --> 00:03:57.097
After that, your screen will be like this.

47
00:03:57.097 --> 00:04:00.397
Now you have to do the signature here.

48
00:04:00.397 --> 00:04:05.497
Just like you do signature with your finger, draw the signature here.

49
00:04:05.497 --> 00:04:09.797
After drawing the signature, click on the save option here.

50
00:04:09.797 --> 00:04:12.597
Signature is simple, you have to do it with your finger.

51
00:04:12.597 --> 00:04:16.397
Just like you do signature, do your signature like this.

52
00:04:16.397 --> 00:04:20.197
After doing the signature, click on save when the signature is correct.

53
00:04:20.197 --> 00:04:24.677
If the signature is wrong, click on redraw and the signature will be deleted.

54
00:04:24.677 --> 00:04:26.677
Now the next step is open.

55
00:04:26.677 --> 00:04:28.677
Now we have to come down.

56
00:04:28.677 --> 00:04:30.677
Do nothing, just click on continue.

57
00:04:30.677 --> 00:04:42.696
Now this step is the final step We just need to complete the e Our account will open successfully

58
00:04:42.696 --> 00:04:48.696
To complete the e-sign, click on the procedure to aadhar e-sign.

59
00:04:48.696 --> 00:04:58.696
Then click on the procedure to aadhar e-sign.

60
00:04:59.536 --> 00:05:01.976
As you can see little detail is displayed here.

61
00:05:03.116 --> 00:05:05.336
If you want to read details, you can do it position of cameras.

62
00:05:07.336 --> 00:05:09.976
After everything is typed, click on the sign in document.

63
00:05:12.176 --> 00:05:12.996
Thank you for watching

64
00:05:17.496 --> 00:05:19.416
Here you can live zoom in screen.

65
00:05:20.636 --> 00:05:21.816
And click the add tab option

66
00:05:23.016 --> 00:05:24.616
STEP 03 Aunt work on the channel

67
00:05:24.616 --> 00:05:37.216
Click on the Aadhar card number and click on send OTP.

68
00:05:37.216 --> 00:05:43.216
Then click on the OTP number on the mobile number linked to your Aadhar card.

69
00:05:43.216 --> 00:05:50.816
After clicking on verify OTP, our account will be successfully opened.

70
00:05:50.816 --> 00:05:54.516
E-sign completed.

71
00:05:54.516 --> 00:05:57.516
Our account has successfully opened.

72
00:05:57.516 --> 00:05:59.516
Click on Continue.

73
00:05:59.516 --> 00:06:01.516
Congratulations is written here.

74
00:06:01.516 --> 00:06:07.556
As soon as we click on the Go to Home page, we will be logged in directly.

